## The Pattern

Direct proofs often rely on **definitions**.

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| Even | $n = 2k$ for some integer $k$ |
| Odd | $n = 2k + 1$ for some integer $k$ |
| Divisible by 3 | $n = 3k$ for some integer $k$ |

Plug in the definition, do the algebra, show what you need.

> **Definition in, result out.**

